<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>단,<sp/>화면<sp/>확인이<sp/>꼭<sp/>필요하면<sp/>매우<sp/>작은<sp/>sample<sp/>app을<sp/>먼저<sp/>추가해도<sp/>된다.</highlight></codeline>
